  }, {
    "tStartMs": 569735,
    "dDurationMs": 3587,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think a lot of companies\nare willing to take."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 573322,
    "dDurationMs": 2419,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Given all the innovation in this space,"
